title: an agent or trustee who receives the rent of or is entrusted with or is concerned with any building
clause_text: an agent or trustee who receives the rent of or is entrusted with or is concerned with any building devoted to religious or charitable purposes; and "Parapet" means a low wall or railing built along the edge of the roof or a floor.
